/mi></math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "T3iS7", "text": "<math><mn>30.2</mn><mo>\u00d7</mo><msup><mrow><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>\u2009\u2009</mtext><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi></math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "<br/><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/nta_abhyas/jee_main/images/ci/image70-3b4fdec0-3d9e-4c8f-8bce-f219ec296697.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%; object-fit:contain\" /> <br/><br/><br/><br/>Let give small displacement to  <math><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">q</mi></math> . The equilibrium will be stable if net force after giving displacement will be in direction of position of equilibrium<br/><br/><br/><br/> <br/><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/nta_abhyas/jee_main/images/ci/image71-49484350-c7a8-4c54-aed9-f60006a5df46.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%; object-fit:contain\" /> <br/><br/><br/><br/> <math><msub><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">F</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi></mrow></msub><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">sin</mi></mrow><mo>\u2061</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">\u03b1</mi></mrow></mrow><mo>\u2265</mo><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">g</mi><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">sin</mi></mrow><mo>\u2061</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">\u03b1</mi></mrow></mrow></math> <br/><br/>then net force will be directed towards vertex i.e. initial equilibrium position<br/><br/> <math><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">k</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">q</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Q</mi></mrow><mrow><msup><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac><mtext>\u2009\u2009</mtext><mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">sin</mi></mrow><mo>\u2061</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">\u03b1</mi></mrow></mrow><mo>\u2265</mo><mi mathvariant=\"no